verses.verse: Yahweh <WH3068> reigns! <WH4427> He is clothed <WH3847> with majesty! <WH1348> Yahweh <WH3068> is armed <WH247> with <WH3847> strength. <WH5797> The world <WH8398> also is established. <WH3559> It can't <WH4131> be moved.
Your throne <WH3678> is established <WH3559> from long ago. <WH227> You are from everlasting. <WH5769>
The floods <WH5104> have lifted up, <WH5375> Yahweh, <WH3068> the floods <WH5104> have lifted up <WH5375> their voice. <WH6963> The floods <WH5104> lift up <WH5375> their waves. <WH1796>
Above the voices <WH6963> of many <WH7227> waters, <WH4325> the mighty <WH117> breakers <WH4867> of the sea, <WH3220> Yahweh <WH3068> on high <WH4791> is mighty. <WH117>
Your statutes <WH5713> stand <WH3966> firm. <WH539> Holiness <WH6944> adorns <WH4998> your house, <WH1004> Yahweh, <WH3068> forevermore. <WH753>
